name: Gemini in its power color
description:
Gemini (May 21–June 20): Yellow 

Go out and take on the world with your zodiac power color that amplifies your inherent nature and boosts your confidence to express yourself more freely. 

Gemini’s bright intellect and radiant personality translate to the color yellow. Like a buzzing bee, this sign is energetic and constantly moving, in body and spirit. “Gemini represents the curiosity of a young child as they learn new things,” Terrones says. Rely on scintillating yellow to inspire and revitalize you, especially in creative spaces like a home studio or workspaces like an office cubicle. Your zodiac sign’s color can transform lackluster surroundings with simple additions like sunflowers and yellow wall art.
